{"tid":2345401,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）有冇人試過膝頭哥發熱？","createTime":"2020-12-29T12:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:51:46.000Z","uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fd22d2390cebd5e6d5d4ee525cb64a89a2e7d185","tid":2345401,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"近依幾個月，唔知點解成日食完飯就發覺自己膝頭哥好熱，小腿同大腿嘅溫度就正常，有冇人知咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：番凍倉工作（但每日都唔會入去超過2個鐘）"},{"pid":"fd3b30f6c38ac33e1354c5e711e3ba8c15ce3bd7","tid":2345401,"uid":325243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beb7e9dbfdc77ca035ff0943e888ed558cc8e74","tid":2345401,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"a8352488fb42c3382538001d04f7c7f326179fa1","tid":2345401,"uid":371177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"已完"},{"pid":"0350defc8e4536261eefb741ff77da802ff845a6","tid":2345401,"uid":45572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"膝頭哥偷食左辣椒醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f484c4c7cf49db8957d3fd3248d716f2a526ab","tid":2345401,"uid":106952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8029ace1eba4d30e6c2826d070b76c69c8f4132","tid":2345401,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"之前屋企人膝頭哥好痛都會發熱<br />\n之後睇醫生話勞損個類，最後做手術換咗個膝頭。總之好大鑊<br />\n建議樓主睇專科，有事起上嚟唔少嘢 <br />\n手尾好長 <br />\n依嫁可以敷冰袋先，醫生都係叫我屋企人敷冰袋"},{"pid":"fbbc215864a242fccbc8f74ee367bbd5db65270a","tid":2345401,"uid":378902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"試過 每次沖完熱水涼都會咁"},{"pid":"ef7bbc999891c7a2719009a2edc69d40623fc99b","tid":2345401,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"上網搵健腰操，上身姿勢不良影響下身支撐。<br />\n首先要解決呢樣。做負重工作要用正確姿勢。"},{"pid":"44d82ad95768605447e1fc3d57b07f458791d515","tid":2345401,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"但奇怪嘅係，我上網查見好多人會話伴隨紅腫痛，但我又淨係熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c9732c52b77ef9b9ec066a6f80036a0243021d","tid":2345401,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d82ad95768605447e1fc3d57b07f458791d515","tid":2345401,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"但奇怪嘅係，我上網查見好多人會話伴隨紅腫痛，但我又淨係熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"發熱有可能係血呀/細胞呀 之類做緊野<br />\n之前膝頭做完手術 消晒腫之後都仲熱左一輪<br />\n但如果係細胞做緊野 即係有野要佢去修復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d5dd003cf050befb448db5c68130d92d8a4ece","tid":2345401,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d82ad95768605447e1fc3d57b07f458791d515","tid":2345401,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"但奇怪嘅係，我上網查見好多人會話伴隨紅腫痛，但我又淨係熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"發炎但神經壞左FEEL唔到<br />\n下世小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a214ef8f07798707dc39637c61fc558560c928","tid":2345401,"uid":227951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"我以前跑過下步都試過發熱 無紅無腫 少少痛<br />\n物理治療師話應該膝頭入面發炎 勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都唔係好清晰 應該我跑得少又唔識跑<br />\n最後休息返 無事"},{"pid":"dd98bdbba989de2e24f1f105aec859a373db5706","tid":2345401,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"發炎 有做運動嘅應該姿勢唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}